high_descs: Turn to the left and move to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of the sink.
Hold the knife and turn around, then turn right to the counter. Look up the cabinets above.
Place the knife in a cup in the upper cabinet.
Take out the cup from the upper cabinet. Shut the door.
Hold the cup and look down to the counter.
Place the cup and knife on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and knife to the counter.

high_descs: Move to the table ahead, then turn left to go to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife from in the sink.
Turn around, step forward, then turn right and walk to the counter, then look up at the cabinet above.
Open the cabinet and put the butter knife in the cup, in the cabinet.
Pick up the cup from the cabinet.
Look down at the counter below.
Put the cup on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the sink
Pick up the bread knife in front of the sink
Turn left then face the cabinet on your right
Open the cabinet then put the knife in the cup
Pick up the knife with cup
Go down and face the counter
Put the cup with knife on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put the cup with knife in the counter
